    <item>
      <title>美联储官员古尔斯比称就业数据显示劳动力市场正在企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/fed-s-goolsbee-says-jobs-data-shows-labor-market-stabilizing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比表示，最新的就业报告表明劳动力市场正在稳定在充分就业水平，并不是经济过热的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/fed-s-goolsbee-says-jobs-data-shows-labor-market-stabilizing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:36:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>融创称不排除进行第二次境外债务重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/sunac-says-it-can-t-rule-out-second-offshore-debt-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约的房地产开发商融创中国控股有限公司表示，由于长期的房地产危机使其前景黯淡，且面临另一份法院要求其清盘的诉讼，它不能排除进行第二次境外债务重组的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/sunac-says-it-can-t-rule-out-second-offshore-debt-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员推迟美联储下次降息，美国 30 年期国债收益率触及 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/treasuries-tumble-as-traders-push-back-next-fed-cut-to-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于劳动力市场韧性增强，交易员将对美联储下次降息的预期转移到今年下半年，美国国债价格暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/treasuries-tumble-as-traders-push-back-next-fed-cut-to-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 13:46:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
